        <h1 id="s00">Tobias Night Review — Executive Summary</h1>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> 27 Mar 2026<br>
        <strong>Scope reviewed:</strong> Production Manager, Video Orchestrator, Branch 1 (Pre-Production), Branch 2 (Audio), Branch 3 (Visual Planning), and general architecture docs.</p>

        <hr>

        <h2 id="s00-what">What I Reviewed</h2>
